@sariyahidan Hi, 
I'm sorry to hear that your luggage wasn't duly delivered. Please contact our colleagues from Feedback Management using this link https://t.co/DlPk2wk146 for any compensation requests. 
Best regards, Gayle

@sunshinekilleen Liebe Anna,
vielen Dank für dein Feedback. Deinen Ärger können wir sehr gut nachvollziehen. Bitte wende dich an unsere Kollegen der Feedback Management Abteilung. Über dieses Fomular kannst du uns dein Anliegen zukommen lassen:  https://t.co/iHLF3V9WGS 
Viele Grüße,Alessandra

@romasars Hi Roma, 
Thank you for getting in touch. Please be informed that we have replied to your post already. 
Best regards, Shawn

@magga_shanti Hi,
I'm sorry to hear that your luggage wasn't duly delivered. The Social Media Team doesn't have access to the baggage system. Please get in touch with the phone number or E-Mail address on your lost baggage report.
Kind regards, Gayle

@JDubb0217 Hi Joe, 
Thank you for your patience. We are happy to hear via your PM that our colleagues from feedback were able to assist you. Thank you for your continued understanding. 
Best regards, Shawn

@EchteLi29292053 Hi there, 
Thank you for getting in touch. Please accept our apology for the inconvenience caused. Please send us your booking code, so we can take a closer look.
Best regards, Shawn

@ErtlAngelika @eugentv Hi there, 
Thank you for getting in touch. We are sorry for the inconvenience. Please try again using our web page for the online check-in process. The issue should have been fixed now. Thank you for your patience.
Best regards, Shawn

@travel_n_me Hi there, 
Thank you for getting in touch. Do you have a booking code for your request? Please send us your booking code via PM. So we can take a closer look.
Best regards, Shawn

@crowleyjo Hello Jo, we are currently experiencing an unusual increase in volume. We want you to know that this is not typical for the type of service we strive to provide our customers. You can send us your booking code in a DM, we'll try to help. 
Best regards
Alessandra

@travel_n_me Dear Krutee,
I've checked your booking and noticed that it was issued by a travel agency. Please contact them for further assistance. 
Best regards, Gayle

@wilcochris Hello Chris,
we open our desks 3 hours before departure.
Best regards, Alessandra
